<dl id="n12147g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12147g">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12147g"> 147(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> with wings <font color="green">[yeesh]</font> &amp; trumpet</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Ainsi appara&icirc;t cette pr&eacute;dication du jugement dernier. Comment se fait-il donc que ma&icirc;tre Vincent Ferrier ait &eacute;t&eacute; repr&eacute;sent&eacute; avec des ailes aux &eacute;paules et une trompette aux l&egrave;vres? Comment se fait-il qu&apos;il ait &eacute;t&eacute; mu&eacute; en un ange apocalyptique? <br><font color="green">[Thus appeared this prophecy of the last judgement. Why is it then that master <mark>Vincent Ferrier</mark> has been represented <mark>with wings on his shoulders and a trumpet at his lips</mark>? How is it that he was changed into an apocalyptic angel?]</font> <small> Matthieu-Maxime Gorce, <a name="STVF" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#STVF"><cite title="source">Saint Vincent Ferrier</cite></a> (1924) 144</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
